Code You Can Directly Port

1. Permission Hook Pattern
From `src/hooks/toolPermission/`:

```typescript
// Claude pattern
export function useToolPermission(tool: Tool, mode: PermissionMode) {
  if (mode === 'bypass') return 'granted';
  if (mode === 'plan' && planModeActive) return 'granted';
  return promptUser(tool);
}
```

Swibe implementation in `visitor.js`:

```javascript
class EthicsValidator {
  validate(toolCall, context) {
    const permission = this.resolvePermission(toolCall, context.mode);
    if (permission === 'deny') throw new EthicsViolation(toolCall);
    if (permission === 'ask') return this.promptUser(toolCall);
    return 'granted';
  }
}
```

2. Streaming Response Handler
From `QueryEngine.ts`:

```typescript
// Claude pattern
async function* streamResponse(prompt: string) {
  const stream = await anthropic.messages.create({...});
  for await (const chunk of stream) {
    yield chunk.delta?.text || '';
    // Tool call detection
    if (chunk.type === 'tool_use') {
      yield { type: 'tool_call', tool: chunk.name, input: chunk.input };
    }
  }
}
```

Swibe enhancement for `think` primitive:

```swibe
